name: How do I see the world V2

metadata.name: Monument Valley
metadata.description: 2020. USA. On the border of Utah and Arizona. The same road on which Forrest Gump ran in the movie of the same name. We spent the night in the car by the side of the road and waited for sunset when there were fewer cars on the road. It was very quiet. Just me and my friend all over the desert and no one else.
